@page "/"

<PageTitle>Manager Dashboard</PageTitle>

<section class="rounded-b-[2rem] border-x border-b border-fuchsia-400/15 bg-gradient-to-br from-black/35 via-[#0b0612]/30 to-[#17081f]/35 p-8 shadow-[0_0_48px_rgba(168,85,247,0.16)] backdrop-blur-[2px]">
    <div class="space-y-8">
        <p class="text-[0.7rem] uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-fuchsia-200/85">Dashboard</p>
        <div>
            <h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-white">Coming soon</h1>
            <p class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-sm leading-7 text-neutral-300">
                This dashboard will become the central place to see other servers info, live fleet state, connection health, and cross-server actions.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid gap-4 lg:grid-cols-3">
            <div class="rounded-[1.75rem] border border-fuchsia-400/15 bg-black/25 p-6 shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(192,132,252,0.14)] backdrop-blur-xl">
                <p class="text-[0.7rem] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-fuchsia-200/85">Servers</p>
                <p class="mt-3 text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Coming soon</p>
                <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-300">Remote server pages will show fleet info, connection status, and per-server visibility from one control panel.</p>
                <a href="/servers" class="mt-4 inline-flex rounded-full border border-fuchsia-300/25 bg-fuchsia-400/10 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-fuchsia-100 transition hover:bg-fuchsia-400/20">
                    Open Servers
                </a>
            </div>

            <div class="rounded-[1.75rem] border border-fuchsia-400/15 bg-black/25 p-6 shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(192,132,252,0.14)] backdrop-blur-xl">
                <p class="text-[0.7rem] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-fuchsia-200/85">VPN</p>
                <p class="mt-3 text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Coming soon</p>
                <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-300">VPN tools will create shared configs and expose the connection details required by the other managed servers.</p>
                <a href="/vpn" class="mt-4 inline-flex rounded-full border border-fuchsia-300/25 bg-fuchsia-400/10 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-fuchsia-100 transition hover:bg-fuchsia-400/20">
                    Open VPN
                </a>
            </div>

            <div class="rounded-[1.75rem] border border-fuchsia-400/15 bg-black/25 p-6 shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(192,132,252,0.14)] backdrop-blur-xl">
                <p class="text-[0.7rem] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-fuchsia-200/85">Settings</p>
                <p class="mt-3 text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Coming soon</p>
                <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-300">Control-app settings will live here, including local manager options, security access, and operator tools.</p>
                <a href="/settings" class="mt-4 inline-flex rounded-full border border-fuchsia-300/25 bg-fuchsia-400/10 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-fuchsia-100 transition hover:bg-fuchsia-400/20">
                    Open Settings
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
